      ◄=============►
       TV Show Notes 
      ◄=============►-----------------------------------------------------►
                                   
          New series. Dave Myers and Simon King travel the UK in search 
          of quality baked British staples ù pies, pastries and cakes.
          They begin by looking at bread and suggesting inexpensive ideas
          for home baking. Among the recipes they demonstrate are a 
          classic brown loaf, a brown ale and cheese bread to serve with
          onion soup, and naan ù to accompany a curry they produce on the 
          shores of a lake 

